---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="SocialProof vs Okendo — Shopify Reviews Comparison | SocialProof" description="Okendo starts at $19/mo but scales steeply to $119+/mo. SocialProof is free to start and $9/mo Pro. See the honest comparison for Shopify store owners." canonical="https://socialproof.dev/vs/okendo">
<style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; margin: 0; background: #fff; color: #111; }
    nav { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 1rem 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
    nav a.logo { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.25rem; color: #111; text-decoration: none; }
    nav .nav-links a { margin-left: 1.5rem; color: #555; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    nav .cta-nav { background: #111; color: #fff !important; padding: .45rem 1rem; border-radius: 6px; }
    .hero { text-align: center; padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .vs-badge { display: inline-block; background: #f0f0f0; color: #555; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .06em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: .35rem .75rem; border-radius: 99px; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
    .hero h1 span { color: #4f46e5; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.15rem; color: #444; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; }
    .hero-cta { display: inline-block; background: #4f46e5; color: #fff; padding: .85rem 2rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem; }
    .hero-cta:hover { background: #3730a3; }
    .price-callout { display: inline-flex; gap: 2rem; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px solid #e5e5e5; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.25rem 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .price-callout .item { text-align: center; }
    .price-callout .item .price { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800; }
    .price-callout .item .label { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #777; margin-top: .2rem; }
    .price-callout .item.vouch .price { color: #4f46e5; }
    .price-callout .item.other .price { color: #dc2626; }
    section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 2rem; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .compare-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .compare-table th { padding: .75rem 1rem; text-align: left; font-size: 0.85rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .05em; color: #888; border-bottom: 2px solid #eee; }
    .compare-table th:nth-child(2) { color: #4f46e5; }
    .compare-table td { padding: .85rem 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; font-size: 0.97rem; vertical-align: top; }
    .compare-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
    .compare-table td:first-child { color: #555; font-weight: 500; }
    .yes { color: #16a34a; font-weight: 600; }
    .no { color: #dc2626; font-weight: 600; }
    .partial { color: #d97706; font-weight: 600; }
    .winner-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .winner-card { border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.75rem; }
    .winner-card.vouch { background: #f0fdf4; border: 1px solid #86efac; }
    .winner-card.other { background: #fafafa; border: 1px solid #e5e5e5; }
    .winner-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 800; margin: 0 0 .75rem; }
    .winner-card ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2rem; }
    .winner-card li { font-size: 0.92rem; color: #444; margin-bottom: .4rem; }
    .savings-box { background: #fffbeb; border: 1px solid #fcd34d; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .savings-box h3 { margin: 0 0 .5rem; font-size: 1rem; }
    .savings-box p { margin: 0; color: #555; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .bottom-cta { text-align: center; background: #4f46e5; color: #fff; border-radius: 16px; padding: 3.5rem 2rem; margin: 3rem 0; }
    .bottom-cta h2 { color: #fff; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .bottom-cta p { color: rgba(255,255,255,.85); margin-bottom: 2rem; font-size: 1.05rem; }
    .cta-white { display: inline-block; background: #fff; color: #4f46e5; padding: .85rem 2rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem; }
    footer { text-align: center; padding: 2rem; color: #999; font-size: 0.85rem; border-top: 1px solid #eee; }
    footer a { color: #999; }
    @media (max-width: 600px) { .winner-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .price-callout { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; } }
</style>
<nav>
  <a class="logo" href="/">SocialProof</a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="/for">For your industry</a>
    <a href="/vs">Compare</a>
    <a href="/#pricing">Pricing</a>
    <a href="/app" class="cta-nav">Try free</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="vs-badge">SocialProof vs Okendo</div>
  <h1>Okendo is built for big Shopify brands. <span>SocialProof is built for everyone else.</span></h1>
  <p>Okendo is great if you're doing $1M+ in Shopify revenue. But if you're a growing store or small business, you'll hit their price wall fast. Here's the honest comparison.</p>
  <div class="price-callout">
    <div class="item vouch"><div class="price">$9/mo</div><div class="label">SocialProof Pro</div></div>
    <div class="item other"><div class="price">$119/mo</div><div class="label">Okendo Essential</div></div>
  </div>
  <a href="/app" class="hero-cta">Try SocialProof free →</a>
</div>

<section>
  <h2>Feature comparison</h2>
  <table class="compare-table">
    <thead><tr><th>Feature</th><th>SocialProof</th><th>Okendo</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>Free tier</td><td class="yes">✓ Forever (1 widget)</td><td class="no">✗ No free tier</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Starting price</td><td class="yes">$9/mo Pro</td><td class="no">$19/mo (50 orders/mo limit)</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Scales to $119/mo</td><td class="yes">✓ Always $9 Pro</td><td class="no">✗ Yes — at 500 orders/mo</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Text testimonials</td><td class="yes">✓</td><td class="yes">✓</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Photo/video reviews</td><td class="no">✗ Text only</td><td class="yes">✓ (higher tiers)</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Embeddable widget</td><td class="yes">✓ Any website</td><td class="partial">Shopify-only</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Works outside Shopify</td><td class="yes">✓ WordPress, Squarespace, etc.</td><td class="no">✗</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Review collection emails</td><td class="yes">✓</td><td class="yes">✓</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Google Shopping integration</td><td class="no">✗</td><td class="yes">✓ (higher tiers)</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Setup time</td><td class="yes">~5 minutes</td><td class="partial">Setup + Shopify install</td></tr>
      <tr><td>No per-order pricing</td><td class="yes">✓ Flat rate</td><td class="no">✗ Scales with orders</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <div class="winner-grid">
    <div class="winner-card vouch">
      <h3>✓ SocialProof wins for…</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Small and mid-size Shopify stores</li>
        <li>Businesses using multiple platforms (not Shopify-only)</li>
        <li>Anyone who wants predictable flat pricing</li>
        <li>Service businesses (agencies, coaches, consultants)</li>
        <li>Getting started without a monthly commitment</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="winner-card other">
      <h3>Okendo wins for…</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>High-volume Shopify stores (1,000+ orders/mo)</li>
        <li>Brands needing Google Shopping syndication</li>
        <li>Enterprise teams with dedicated review strategy</li>
        <li>Shopify Plus merchants</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="savings-box">
    <h3>💸 The math: Okendo vs SocialProof at 500 orders/month</h3>
    <p>At 500 orders/month, Okendo charges $119/month. SocialProof Pro is $9/month — flat, forever. That's $1,320/year back in your pocket. For a growing Shopify store, that's a meaningful difference.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>When does Okendo make sense?</h2>
  <p>Okendo is a genuinely good product — but it's engineered for scale. The moment you exceed their order thresholds, pricing jumps. If you're running a high-volume Shopify brand with a full marketing team, Okendo's Google Shopping feeds and loyalty integrations are worth it.</p>
  <p>But if you're a founder wearing all the hats, running a service business, or building your store to that level — you don't need Okendo yet. You need something that works now, is free to start, and doesn't punish you for growing.</p>
  <p>SocialProof collects testimonials, displays them beautifully, and works on any website. It's designed for the stage you're actually at.</p>
</section>

<div class="bottom-cta">
  <h2>Start collecting testimonials today — free</h2>
  <p>No per-order pricing. No Shopify-only lock-in. Free forever for 1 active widget.</p>
  <a href="/app" class="cta-white">Get started free →</a>
</div>

<footer>
  <p>© 2025 SocialProof · <a href="/privacy">Privacy</a> · <a href="/terms">Terms</a> · <a href="/vs">Compare all tools</a></p>
</footer>

<div class="footer-links" style="margin-top:2rem;padding-top:1.5rem;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;font-size:0.9rem;">
  <strong style="color:#374151;">Also explore:</strong>
  <a href="/for/coaches" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Coaches</a>
  <a href="/for/freelancers" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Freelancers</a>
  <a href="/for/ecommerce" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Ecommerce</a>
  <a href="/vs/senja" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">vs Senja</a>
  <a href="/vs/testimonial" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">vs Testimonial.to</a>
</div>
</Base>
